               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17970426-77-cd425" type="crimeDate">21st of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17970426-77-off424 t17970426-77-cd425"></join>, a pair of copper scales, value 4s. and a quarter of a pound weight, value 3d.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t17970426-77-victim619" type="victimName">
                  James 
                  Mayne
               <interp inst="t17970426-77-victim619" type="surname" value="Mayne"></interp>
